The '''''Kooba's Pride''''' was a starliner that operated along [[Keller's Void/Legends|Keller's Void]]. The ship was seized by [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] who used an [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] as a natural [[Interdictor/Legends|interdictor]].

